cff-version: 1.2.0
title: "MecaNano — Machine Learning for Nanomechanics (Tutorial 1)"
message: "If you use this repository or its data, please cite it (and the underlying dataset)."
type: software
version: 1.0.0
date-released: "2026-07-12"
