repository-code: "https://github.com/edrossi93/mecanano-ml-nanomechanics"
url: "https://github.com/edrossi93/mecanano-ml-nanomechanics"
abstract: >-
  A hands-on, beginner-first tutorial on machine learning for nanoindentation and
  materials data: runnable notebooks covering features and PCA, clustering,
  supervised models and honest evaluation, CNNs and autoencoders, correlative
  registration and multimodal label transfer, coating and substrate deconvolution,
  uncertainty quantification, microstructure segmentation, and Bayesian
  optimization, on public and synthetic datasets.
keywords:
  - nanoindentation
  - high-speed nanoindentation mapping
  - machine learning
  - materials science
  - materials informatics
  - thin films and coatings
  - convolutional neural networks
  - uncertainty quantification
  - image segmentation
  - Bayesian optimization
